product_name: Probalance Toothbrush Parsley & Mint Large Dog Treat
name: Probalance Toothbrush Parsley & Mint Large Dog Treat 15Pk
description:
ProBalance is developed by our team of expert nutritionists and veterinary scientists to help your pet thrive through a balance of nature and science.

Treat your dog and support their oral health with these dental toothbrush treats, that have been deliciously designed to help clean teeth & freshen breath in a parsley & mint flavour dogs love. The toothbrush shape & texture helps scrub away plaque & tartar, whilst parsley & peppermint oil help freshen breath. Rapidly absorbing Vitamin C promotes gum health and more effective plaque removal. These dental treats are easy to digest and gentle on stomachs.

All ProBalance treats have no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.
